title: FDR: American Tyrant: The Shocking 'Rap Sheet' of Franklin Delan
description:
Among America's Establishment historians, Franklin Delano Roosevelt is almost universally regarded as America's "greatest President". But is this an accurate assessment, or historical propaganda,

The purpose of 'FDR: American Tyrant' is not to review FDR's economic failures and lies (though there were plenty), but rather to focus solely on the tyrannical actions of FDR's Presidency.

Most of FDR's modern day conservative detractors are not even fully aware of just how heavy FDR's hand was. Liberals are often shocked when they hear the full extent of FDR's tyranny (though many will find some sick intellectual contortion in order to rationalize these deeds.)

This work presents, in chronological order, FDR's 16 worst acts of dictatorial tyranny. Judge for yourself
